"        0",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        1",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        2",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        3",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        4",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        5",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        6. Over the past month, how often have you had to push or strain to begin urination?",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        0",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        1",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        2",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        3",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        4",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        5",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"      <tr>",
"       <td>",
"        7. Over the past month, how many times did you most typically",
"get up to urinate from the time you went to bed at night until the time",
"you got up in the morning?",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
